casebody.data:
Prescillano MARTINEZ and Madardo Abeyta v. Rebecca MAESTAS et al. No. 2134. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit June 13, 1940. Robert H. LaFollette, of Albuquerque, N. M., for appellants. Gilbert & Hamilton, of Santa Fe, N. M., for appellees.

Before PHILLIPS and LEWIS, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed, on motion of appellees, at appellants’ costs, for failure to prosecute.
